Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.40,日文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}始めようよ　さあ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:04.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What a Wonderful Dream!!
